quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,Truly We have granted you a clear victory
  48,2,"so that Allah may forgive you your earlier errors and any later ones and complete His blessing upon you, and guide you on a Straight Path"
  48,3,and so that Allah may help you with a mighty help
  48,4,"It is He who sent down serenity into the hearts of the muminun thereby increasing their iman with more iman — the legions of the heavens and the earth belong to Allah. Allah is All-Knowing, All-Wise —"
  48,5,"so that He may admit the men and women of the muminun into Gardens with rivers flowing under them, remaining in them timelessly, for ever, and erase their bad actions from them; and in Allah´s sight that is a mighty victory"
  48,6,"And so that He might punish the men and women of the hypocrites and the men and women of the idolaters — those who think bad thoughts about Allah. They will suffer an evil turn of fate. Allah is angry with them, and has cursed them and prepared Hell for them. What an evil destination"
  48,7,"The legions of the heavens and the earth belong to Allah. Allah is Almighty, All-Wise"
  48,8,"We have sent you bearing witness, bringing good news and giving warning"
  48,9,so that you might all have iman in Allah and His Messenger and honour Him and respect Him and glorify Him in the morning and the evening